                    <item name="SourceCount" type_name="gh_int32" type_code="3">0</item>
                    <item name="UserText" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">Description
Applies chosen facade block to simple building massings. Intended to add facade options over time across definition versions

Notes
  Intended for masterplans &amp; context modelling for visualisations
Works with flat volumes
Currently assumes 3m floor-to-floor height, and will try to scale block modules to fill gaps (smaller modules work best - above 4m gets tricky)
  
Dependencies
Rhino 8 (in meters)
Pufferfish (food4rhino.com/en/app/pufferfish)</item>
